{"type": "article", "id": 3188, "title": "暗藏玄机的边桌", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-31T08:05:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523282132YGRqkLN8pQoAV9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自德国汉堡的设计工作室 Herr M 受到儿童益智玩具的启发，推出了一款名为 Schiebepuzzle 的边桌。整体外形来看，Schiebepuzzle 就是一个普通的立方体，但仔细究其内里，你会发现暗藏玄机，边桌的表面是一个可以左右上下滑动的门板，一个个隐藏的隔间可以存放报纸杂志、葡萄酒、杯垫以及眼镜等日常生活杂物。是不是有种玩捉迷藏的感觉？这也正是这款边桌设计的乐趣所在。定价 520 欧元，<a href=\"http://fraeulein-m.com/Produkte/Schiebepuzzle.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232817gYnqPltbpfBTXdzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232817ra7k9s4LxDcW3XzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232818bBoM7dAWLrvIqyzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232818qRHelXZviS8QtEuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232819fO0NFnWJuoHEeZQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}